# Infrastructure — Conventions

## Before writing

Read `docs/infrastructure.md` before touching infrastructure files.

## After modifying, update

- Port/URL change → `docs/infrastructure.md` § Network
- New secret → `docs/infrastructure.md` § Secrets + security rule
- New/modified container → `docs/infrastructure.md` § Container stack
- Network change → verify references in other docs
